      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "961-983",
      "markText": "忘记历史就意味着背叛。走进历史才能看清历史。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=32282620&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=961&rangeEnd=983",
